Name: Il Sole e la Luna
About the game: Plot IL SOLE E LA LUNA One day in a distant Kingdom, two brothers, Sunny and Moony, they were training for the youth. But they do not know what to do in a fantastic adventure awaits them! GAME DESCRIPTION Adventure Fantasy RPG IL SOLE E LA LUNA Spectacular RPG set in a fantasy era! Choose your class: hero, warrior, magician, priest. Level up, develop equipment, find lots of secrets, find all weapons and defeat mighty gods! Help Sunny and Moony save the kingdom from an unexpected threat! Game Features: Turn-based battles, Hunts, Quest, Open World!
